const deepDive = {
  heading: "Why the Clima Mini Heater Is Our #1 Pick",
  body: [
    "The Clima earns the top spot on flexibility rather than raw power. It plugs directly into a wall outlet with no installation, no assembly and no tools, and it's small enough to unplug and carry to another room in seconds. If your actual problem is 'the room I'm sitting in is cold' — a home office in the morning, a bedroom at night, a nursery — that's the problem it's built for, and it covers up to about 200 square feet.",
